+# SABER LoRA Attack Eval Notes
+
+## Scope
+
+This run reproduces SABER attack-agent inference from the authors' released LoRA adapters, without training.
+
+Hard constraints:
+
+- Do not run `train_vla.py` or `scripts/run_train.sh`.
+- Do not use hand-written perturbation JSON.
+- Generate attack records through `eval_attack_vla.py`.
+- Keep large models, caches, and datasets under `/data0/ldx`.
+- Keep workspace files and attack record JSON under this SABER repo.
+- Use mirror endpoints for external downloads where possible.
+
