+## Operational Notes
+
+- ART reporting `step 0` is acceptable here because the LoRA adapter has already been merged into `--attack_base_model`.
+- If generated records have no perturbation or empty `tools_used`, inspect the vLLM/tool-call parser behavior and keep `max_seq_length=8192`.
+- Port `8000` was busy during this run; use explicit `--attack_server_port` values such as `18000`, `18001`, and `18002`.
+- GPU0 had substantial existing usage during this run. GPU4 was used successfully for Pi0.5, and GPU2/3 were used for the attack agent/vLLM.
+- `action_inflation` with `--select_max_attack_steps` is useful for best-of-N reporting but does not preserve all 10 rollout attempts in `per_episode`.
+
